title: PTI’s Naeem ul Haq bashes Jang/Geo group
text:
PTI’s Naeem ul Haq bashes Jang/Geo group   
PTI’s tussle with Jang/Geo group continuous and takes a new turn when Geo emphasis on the word Muslim when reporting Yesterday’s London incident. 
Here is the exact tweet and you be the judge, If he justifies in accusing them Shameful.Jang emphasises London attackers religion as Muslim in headline ignoring Christian Trumps attack in Syria killing 33 civilians. 
— Naeem ul Haque (@naeemul_haque) March 23, 2017 loading...
